{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"49f69bb5fb","title":"我们愿意向世界上所有国家学习","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"71d950d463","index":0,"year":1956,"month":4,"day":10,"articleId":"49f69bb5fb"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"4074a2b972","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东和丹麦驻华大使金·阿·格瑞杰生谈话的一部分。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3da7139522","type":"title","text":"我们愿意向世界上所有国家学习口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"4074a2b972","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东主席（以下简称毛）：你在北京某多久了？","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"6dfa2364d6","type":"paragraph","text":"金·阿·格瑞杰生大使（以下简称格）：已经有三年了。我很喜欢北京。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"056fce28dd","type":"paragraph","text":"我真诚地希望我们两国之间的关系获得发展。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"4c98b9e2fe","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我们两国之间过去没有打过仗，将来会打仗吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"c59dfae1e1","type":"paragraph","text":"格：不会的。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"fd87408f86","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们不是参加大西洋联盟的国家吗？要是美国打起仗来，你们怎么样呢？","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"639b75ac79","type":"paragraph","text":"格：那不会的。我们两国之间将来也不会打仗。中国作为世界的大国而出现，使和平得救了。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"ef19596542","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：中国不过是个马马虎虎的国家，地方大，力量并不强。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"a8a3ffdcb0","type":"paragraph","text":"格：中国地方大，有一千二百多万平方公里，而丹麦只有四万多平方公里。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"67c418f5fa","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：中国地方没有那么大。如果每一平方公里都像你们国家那样发达就好了。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"3c13e8ca84","type":"paragraph","text":"格：中国还有六亿人口理！","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"2b8ded3cb9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：中国是不会向别人翘尾巴的。如果中国翘尾巴，你们可以批评。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"8705f3b56e","type":"paragraph","text":"格：那自然不会的。至于丹麦，地方虽小，但论单位面积，还经营得不坏。我愿提请主席注意，中国将派两个代表团去丹麦考察农业和合作社。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"0708a1577e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我们很愿意向你们学习，我们愿意向世界上所有国家学习。如果美国人愿意的话，我们也愿意向他们学习。每个国家都有值得学习的长处。我们也愿意向冰岛学习。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"e341a36d00","type":"paragraph","text":"格：冰岛只有渔业，农业很少。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"7e5a25b109","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：渔业就值得学习。","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"73e8b1d6aa","type":"paragraph","text":"格：希望中国代表团去丹麦考察回来后介绍一下丹麦的情况。","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"6c9e597a1a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：需要在报上介绍介绍。你们老呆在北京，知识也受到限制。我想，驻北京的使节们每年五一和十一以后（就是春耕、秋收以后），可以组织两次旅行，到中国各地去看看。你觉得怎么样？","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"a35e43a1f3","type":"paragraph","text":"格：这个主意很好。","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"},{"id":"d7db0a05d3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我们也要学一学你们是怎么办合作社的。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb"}],"page":{"id":"e55fef4a36","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"49f69bb5fb","start":278,"end":279}}}},"__N_SSG":true}